  "title": "Robotic Operations Specialist",
  "description": "<p>What you will do</p><ul><li>Operate and support on-site delivery robots</li><li>Support customers within assigned buildings</li><li>Perform simple daily robot checks </li><li>Keep basic digital delivery records via backend systems</li></ul><p>Why join QuikBot</p><ul><li>Opportunity to work with real robots</li><li>Stable, full-time position</li><li>On-the-job training</li><li>Career growth in robotics operations</li><li>Possibly overseas exposure</li></ul><p>Who we are looking out for</p><ul><li>N Level / NITEC/ Higher NITEC/ Diploma</li><li>No robotic experience required</li><li>Open-minded people willing to work with a growing start up</li><li>Training provided</li></ul><p>Remuneration package will be based on relevant experience. </p>",
